external_knowledge:
Active weather stations refer to stations with a status of 'active'; 
Users can access precipitation data from weather stations; 
Access events are recorded in the access_logs table; 
Precipitation data is stored in data files; 
Data files are linked to weather stations.

- 'treasure trove of data' refers to the weather station with the highest average data file size and total accesses combined;
- 'largest average chest of files' refers to the highest average file size;
- 'most frequent visits' refers to the highest total access count.
